==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncord
<hw>Un*cord"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>cord</ets>.]</ety> <def>To release from cords; to
loosen the cord or cords of; to unfasten or unbind; <as>as, to
<ex>uncord</ex> a package</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncork</ent>⟦br⟧
